<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="utf-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">

  <style>
      @import url('https://fonts.googleapis.com/css?family=Alata');

      html {
          /* Inspired by https://www.swyx.io/css-100-bytes */
          line-height: 1.75;
          font-size: 1em;
          padding: 1.5em 2em;
          background-color: #181A1B;
      }

      body {
          font-family: 'Alata', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', Calibri, sans-serif;
          height: 100%;
          box-sizing: border-box;
          max-width: 70ch;
          color: whitesmoke;
      }

      button {
          font-family: 'Alata', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', Calibri, sans-serif;
          padding: 5px 20px;
          font-size: 1em;
          border: 0;
          border-radius: 5px;
          color: whitesmoke;
          text-align: center;
          vertical-align: middle;
          cursor: pointer;
          background-color: #006633;
      }

      input[type="email"] {
          font-family: 'Alata', -apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, Oxygen, Ubuntu, Cantarell, 'Open Sans', 'Helvetica Neue', Calibri, sans-serif;
          padding: 2px 10px;
          margin-top: 10px;
          font-size: 1em;
          border-color: #006633;
          border-width: 1px;
          border-radius: 5px;
          display: block;
          min-width: 30%;
          background-color: transparent;
      }

      a {
          color: whitesmoke;
      }
  </style>
  <title>Purge started!</title>
</head>
<body>

<p>
  All done, <%= current_user["username"] %>!
</p>

<p>
  We've started your purge. We'll send you an email at <%= email %> when it's done.
</p>

Note: we've got quite a few people purging at the moment, so it might take a while (Twitter's API limits), but we'll definitely get this done!

</body>
</html>